NEW CLUB POSITIONS AVAILABLE!

Pueblo Science is a nonprofit charity that aims to improve STEM education in local, national, and international communities. Our club works very closely with the parent organization by helping with events, fundraising, and spreading awareness. As a club, Pueblo Science U of T aims to develop and facilitate educational and engaging events that promote the importance of STEM and contribute to breaking down the barriers that prevent individuals from pursuing their STEM-related passions.

If you are passionate about STEM and wish to improve its education in local communities, check out the opportunities we have available to join our team! Applications are due by August 28, 11:59 PM EST.
